      • maxUnrolling

        public static int maxUnrolling
        the maximum number that loop unrolling is up to

      • exitCode

        public static int exitCode
        the exit code of compilation

        It is the value returned as a command-line tool. 0 represents normal exit, and negative numbers represent compilation errors.
